genresAdvancedInfo.name: musica gaucha
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Musica gaucha is a traditional music genre from Argentina, Uruguay, and southern Brazil. It is characterized by the use of guitars, drums, and other instruments. The lyrics often revolve around the lifestyle of the gauchos, the cowboys of the region, and their traditions, such as horse riding, cattle herding, and rural life.
